Noun Damage: prism mark
   Wear-Off: The crystal outline around you fractures and fades.
Acquisition:
   - Magi: level 3
Description:
   Prism Mark is the Magi's first defensive utility spell. The caster marks
   a target — typically themselves — with a glittering crystalline outline
   of magical energy. The mark provides a small absorption shield that
   intercepts a portion of incoming damage before the target's health is
   reduced.

   Prism Mark is the Magi's earliest access to magical protection, available
   at the very beginning of their career. While the absorption value is
   modest compared to later shields, it provides meaningful damage mitigation
   at low levels where every point of absorption matters. The crystal outline
   shatters and fades when fully depleted, indicating the mark has been
   consumed by absorbed damage.
*******************************************************************************
